 you are <br>\r\nlooking for a more exclusive or <br>\r\ncustomized experience, <br>\r\nbook a private tour today!  </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"center\">\r\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-orange btn-md\">Book Now</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 col-xs-12\">\r\n                \r\n                    <h3 class=\"center\">Gift Certificates</h3>\r\n                <div class=\"box-inner\">\r\n                     <img src=\"http://foodloverstour.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/002.jpg\" />\r\n                    <p>The perfect gift for a loved one <br>Give the gift of Food! Buy a gift  <br>\r\ncertificatefor one of the London <br>\r\nFood Lover tours.   </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"center\">\r\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-orange btn-md\">Book Now</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n            <div class=\"col-md-4 col-xs-12\">\r\n                \r\n                    <h3 class=\"center\">Our Customers Say</h3>\r\n                <div class=\"box-inner\">\r\n                    <img src=\"http://foodloverstour.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/003.jpg\" />\r\n                    <p>“It was perfect day for me, I can\'t <br>\r\nrecommend it enough…There\'s <br>\r\nno doubt it will quickly become the <br>\r\nhottest tour in town!”\r\n </p>\r\n                    <div class=\"center\">\r\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-orange btn-md\">Book Now</a>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            \r\n        </div>\r\n        <br>\r\n        <div class=\"center\">See our reviews on tripadvisor and keep up with the latest news on our blog.</div>\r\n        <br> \";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:6;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Book Tour Now\";s:4:\"text\";s:48:\"<a href=\"#\" class=\"book-tour\">Book Your Tour</a>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:7;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"CUSTOMER REVIEWS\";s:4:\"text\";s:792:\"<div class=\"box-center\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper-img\"><img width=\"\" src=\"http://foodloverstour.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/reivew01.png\"></div>\r\n<div  class=\"rate\">\r\n<span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star rated\" ></span><span  class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star rated\"></span><span  class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star rated\"></span><span  class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star rated\"></span><span  class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-star rated\"></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><i>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the . Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy.Lorem</i></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\"color:#8c8c8c\">Ingrid Vasques Restelli, Brazil</strong></p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-black btn-md\" href=\"http://foodloverstour.wpengine.com/reviews/\">MORE REAL REVIEWS</a>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:8;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"ABOUT FOOD LOVERS\";s:4:\"text\";s:414:\"<div class=\"box-center\">\r\n<div class=\"wrapper-img\"><img width=\"\" src=\"http://foodloverstour.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/about1.png\"></div>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p>\r\nWe are not just tour guides, we are “Food Lovers” and \r\ntogether we’ll discover and explore London’s most interesting food offerings – and the culture and story behind it.\r\n</p>\r\n<a class=\"btn btn-black btn-md\" href=\"#\">ABOUT US</a>\r\n</div>\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:10;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"About Food Lovers\";s:4:\"text\";s:284:\"London Food Lovers provide Food tours &amp; cultural walking around London. Join one of our group or private tours and enjoy a unique gastronomic and cultural\r\nexperience with a wide variety of incredible foods, and share the history, cultures, and stories, that go with those foods\r\n\";s:6:\"filter\";b:0;}i:11;a:3:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Privacy Polic\";s:4:\"text\";s:866:\"<!-- Button trigger modal -->\r\n<button cla